bmg - Bike Mileage Get

USAGE:
    bmg [-bike=bike] [-start=YYYY/MM/DD] [-end=YYYY/MM/DD] [-group=group]

DESCRIPTION:
    Get and analyze bike mileage statistics. Can filter by bike,
    date range, and group results by various criteria.

OPTIONS:
    -bike=bike
        Filter by specific bike name

    -start=YYYY/MM/DD
        Start date for filtering (alias: -s)

    -end=YYYY/MM/DD
        End date for filtering (alias: -e)

    -group=group
        Group results by (alias: -g):
        bike    - Group by bike
        year    - Group by year
        month   - Group by month
        day     - Group by day

EXAMPLES:
    bmg
    bmg -bike=mountain-bike
    bmg -start=2025/01/01 -end=2025/12/31
    bmg -group=bike
    bmg -bike=road-bike -group=month
